casebody.data:
No. 11-5829. Steven M. Jacob, Petitioner v. Robert P. Houston, Director, Nebraska Department of Correctional Services. 565 U.S. 961, 132 S. Ct. 457,

181 L. Ed. 2d 291,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7525. October 17, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
